## Notes
- The original demo uses `assets.aceternity.com` CDN images — replaced with Unsplash URLs for portability.
- The grid uses a fixed `size-[1720px]` with `scale-50/75/100` responsive scaling. On screens smaller than `lg`, the grid appears at 50–75% scale; ensure the parent has `overflow-hidden` to clip the oversized grid.
- `transform-3d` is a Tailwind utility for `transform-style: preserve-3d` — requires Tailwind v3.3+ or add `[transform-style:preserve-3d]` directly.
- Provide at least 8 images (2 per column) for the marquee to look full; fewer images will leave empty column slots.
